========================================================================
                      NOVA SENTINEL AGENT SETUP (MSI)
========================================================================
Thank you for downloading the NovaSentinel Agent Installer!

This is a mock installer file generated for development, demonstration,
and evaluation purposes.

In a production environment, this binary is compiled as a WiX Installer
(MSI) package for Windows systems (x64) and digitally signed. It
installs the background agent service, registers it with Windows Services,
and prompts for email registration to pair the device with your account.

Setup & Deployment Capabilities:
--------------------------------
1. Installs lightweight background scanning service.
2. Automates weekly scheduled diagnostic runs.
3. Automatically registers startup hooks.
4. Seamlessly pairs with the SaaS telemetry database.

